<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1046> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1046" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. ([- - - -] n. Noctua abd.); Degrassi, 40f., 112, 428f. Abdicated for reasons unknown. The name of his colleague is not preserved. See 289, Censors." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1022> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1022" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Chr. 354 (Corvino II et Noctua); Fast. Hyd. (Maximo et Noctuo); Chr. Pasc. ({Gr}); Cassiod.; Degrassi 112, 428f. On Valerius, see Lübker 50, no. 50." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1021> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1021" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On the name of Valerius, see Fast. Cap. on 312 and 307; on that of Caedicius, see Fast. Cap. on 283 and the filiation of his son, the Consul of 256. In Chr. Pasc. Caedicius has been confused with Decius Mus." .
